{"tid":2163861,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"愛知縣女性於自宅發現骸骨 懷疑是失蹤5年的同居兄長","createTime":"2020-08-19T02:02:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T16:41:13.000Z","uid":4618,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ac05aa83696fe79c58b187dc3318392701877594","tid":2163861,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T02:02:35.000Z","msg":"8月15日愛知縣春日井市某住宅發生骸骨發現案，懷疑屍體屬於住在該宅的一名男子。該名男子在四年前已被列為失蹤人口。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/news_sokuhou/status/1294843588614877185?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnews_sokuhou%2Fstatus%2F1294843588614877185%3Fs%3D21&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5lUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=dad33359\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnews_sokuhou%2Fstatus%2F1294843588614877185%3Fs%3D21&h=d13a3909\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/news_sokuhou/status/1294843588614877185?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n愛知縣警8月15日下午五時接春日井市一名69歲女性報警求肋，指自己在房間內發現疑似人骨。警察到場後在凌亂的房間中找到已經白骨化、沒有穿著衣服的遺體。<br />\n<br />\n據女性所述，她和一兄一弟三人一同居住，兄長在五年前失蹤，並在四年前列作失蹤人口。女性當時正在打掃兄長的房間，其後在房間內發現已經白骨化的遺體。警方相信這具遺體很大機會是女性失蹤多年的兄長，確認死者身分和調查工作仍在進行中。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xdiHrus.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxdiHrus.jpg&h=f1e5421c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b3902a511fffd053a7989401e37cf21976f680b","tid":2163861,"uid":105678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T02:03:38.000Z","msg":"可以動畫化的劇情"},{"pid":"ac7de8f3838e184fbde2b5330812a397f9a67722","tid":2163861,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T02:03:54.000Z","msg":"補汁<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.likejapan.com/life/bones-in-home/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Flife%2Fbones-in-home%2F&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5lUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=59fbffb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.likejapan.com/life/bones-in-home/</a>"},{"pid":"be1443d8a9b67930465afd59c75add0d6f1c7a7